Id.Description: The identifier of the object(s) that are being requested. When searching for a STIX Object, this is a STIX ID.

Type.Description: The type of the object(s) that are being requested. Only the types listed in this parameter are permitted in the response.

Version.Description: The version(s) of the object(s) that are being requested from either an object or manifest endpoint.

SpecVersion.Description: The specification version(s) of the STIX object that are being requested.
